
Fact buyer 
Fact seller

Fact party Derived from buyer When Holds(buyer)
                      , seller When Holds(seller)

Fact taxable Identified by party
  Holds when income > 10000 && income-of()
           , capital > 50000 && capital-of()

Fact income Identified by Int
  Derived from income-of.income
Fact capital Identified by Int
  Derived from capital-of.capital

Fact income-of Identified by party * income
Fact capital-of Identified by party * capital
